42 “(a) Churches and cemeteries in conjunction with churches.
43 “(b) The propagation or harvesting of a forest product.
44 “(c) Utility facilities necessary for public service, not including commercial facilities for the
45 purpose of generating electrical power for public use by sale or transmission towers over 200 feet
